{"tid":1380421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[和理非請入]其實行完番屋企，除左睇直播做冷氣軍師，仲可以做呢樣野","createTime":"2019-07-29T04:19:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T13:49:29.000Z","uid":192851,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6340d585f7d8b14b38922f9e3e87b0d33a0eb9e3","tid":1380421,"uid":192851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:19:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就係喺港鐵站接放學</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你唔一定有車，但學天水圍人咁，喺自己港鐵站報告下站內站外，關心下手足，幫佢哋拍卡出閘，同閘拍入拍出只係幾蚊，雖然每次都要等幾分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n唔少學生有勇有謀，係因為街上手足多，但番到屋企附近，未必有咁多朋友一齊，會驚好多。<br />\n<br />\n狗車唔可能即刻派去所有站，一定係重點某啲站，喺所有出口/站台守，愈快有消息出街，就愈能夠be water去其他安全既站走。<br />\n<br />\n無論係護送，站哨，趕狗，拍片，定只係望住手足默默打氣，前線好需要大家幫佢地安心回家休息。<br />\n<br />\nps其實除左旺角，仲有好多好好既中轉站: 美孚，沙田，黃大仙，觀塘<br />\n<br />\n最後: <br />\n<br />\n勇武同和理非＝男女朋友，床頭打交床尾和<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1376065\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1376065</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d9ece2e436b0fb94234940d3c21740a70ef598b8","tid":1380421,"uid":192851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:21:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1f3b7c65ea5f1c3d67f2ed8a7e5663a7f5e39483","tid":1380421,"uid":192851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:23:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f194690723645757c5c2fc5a1f712a937e519c04","tid":1380421,"uid":229566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:24:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"60f5848788a27ded659db68c446e17eb789e4bb7","tid":1380421,"uid":192851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:27:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"365437978df6c367fbee05daa01a0e0e2bdadbec","tid":1380421,"uid":20725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:30:47.000Z","msg":"可行 或轉場"},{"pid":"870122083244dcd34df99c281c35e87e618e46cc","tid":1380421,"uid":264165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:42:58.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n有d咩可以做都一定盡做"},{"pid":"3ace3021e259ea079a0745b23373eb562c7daabd","tid":1380421,"uid":192851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:10:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"41c031132481647049eba12b7a6becbed0af452d","tid":1380421,"uid":67332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:19:02.000Z","msg":"8月5號齊罷工"},{"pid":"b54a3eca7a92a9939ec2084ca62b1e3822d36dcc","tid":1380421,"uid":192851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:24:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"263ecf95a7c933960b02125cfebdb6923ac369f3","tid":1380421,"uid":46128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:29:49.000Z","msg":"同站出入係扣十蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />買多啲單程飛幫手好啲"},{"pid":"b9c6a2aba7692091475e6e16cfbbf02764899025","tid":1380421,"uid":60449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"263ecf95a7c933960b02125cfebdb6923ac369f3","tid":1380421,"uid":46128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:29:49.000Z","msg":"同站出入係扣十蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />買多啲單程飛幫手好啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:37:29.000Z","msg":"唔建議直接跳閘"},{"pid":"87b264735957a980df586d6b7ef406d616f8c644","tid":1380421,"uid":192851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"263ecf95a7c933960b02125cfebdb6923ac369f3","tid":1380421,"uid":46128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:29:49.000Z","msg":"同站出入係扣十蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />買多啲單程飛幫手好啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:05:36.000Z","msg":"只要喺短時間內同站只係扣4蚊，每次出同入中間要隔一分鐘<br />\n<br />\n而且就算十蚊，我都肯幫大家比，100個都比"},{"pid":"c36b453f482a13dc404a5bebf46ddb50585a35f8","tid":1380421,"uid":192851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"263ecf95a7c933960b02125cfebdb6923ac369f3","tid":1380421,"uid":46128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:29:49.000Z","msg":"同站出入係扣十蚊<img src=\"/